        "content": "<p>Hey all, <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"421591\">@Bailey Hayes</span> and I have just finished the bulk of the migration to the <a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI\">WASI monorepo</a>, and it is now up and running!</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/2f0822f821a417e59c2ce1532876502b5d38ee2b/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f366561653862303938646261303035333135633837356230343731393863396532616330623633663163613166306132343231653034373461396362633466632f576562417373656d626c792f57415349&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI\" title=\"GitHub - WebAssembly/WASI: WebAssembly System Interface\">GitHub - WebAssembly/WASI: WebAssembly System Interface</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">WebAssembly System Interface. Contribute to WebAssembly/WASI development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></div></div>",
        "id": 560281436,
        "sender_full_name": "Yosh Wuyts",
        "timestamp": 1764120195
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>All existing proposals have been migrated, issues have been moved too, and outstanding PRs closed. All proposal champions will have received invites for the monorepo as well.</p>",
        "id": 560281566,
        "sender_full_name": "Yosh Wuyts",
        "timestamp": 1764120272
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>We're still putting the finishing touches on the repo, including setting up code owners and recreating CI. PRs for both have been filed, just not merged yet. I expect us to turn that around in the next day or so.</p>",
        "id": 560281686,
        "sender_full_name": "Yosh Wuyts",
        "timestamp": 1764120332
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>You can find all the phase 3 proposals listed under the <a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/tree/main/proposals\"><code>proposals/</code> directory</a> in the WASI repo.</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/tree/main/proposals\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/2f0822f821a417e59c2ce1532876502b5d38ee2b/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f366561653862303938646261303035333135633837356230343731393863396532616330623633663163613166306132343231653034373461396362633466632f576562417373656d626c792f57415349&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/tree/main/proposals\" title=\"WASI/proposals at main · WebAssembly/WASI\">WASI/proposals at main · WebAssembly/WASI</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">WebAssembly System Interface. Contribute to WebAssembly/WASI development by creating an account on GitHub.</div></div></div>",
        "id": 560282005,
        "sender_full_name": "Yosh Wuyts",
        "timestamp": 1764120534
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Either way! - We got the bulk of the migration done today, and even managed to bring over the project history too!</p>",
        "id": 560282213,
        "sender_full_name": "Yosh Wuyts",
        "timestamp": 1764120657
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Wanted to make sure to let y'all know. And we'll share an update here too once we have CI up as well.</p>",
        "id": 560282434,
        "sender_full_name": "Yosh Wuyts",
        "timestamp": 1764120796
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>as I mentioned <a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/pull/826#issuecomment-3577093416\">here</a>, the migration inadvertently closed a bunch of unrelated issues since they happen to share the issue numbers with issues from the original repos that a commit mentioned as closing.</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/pull/826#issuecomment-3577093416\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.net/ecdb6dd42e974b4c9f175d5505da84c1ba6dfd0f/68747470733a2f2f6f70656e67726170682e6769746875626173736574732e636f6d2f653037653335366165303336616233653231303139663334316632343863326161323833613631373939313062363862343962353832343435643537356234622f576562417373656d626c792f574153492f70756c6c2f383236&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/pull/826#issuecomment-3577093416\" title=\"Migrate proposals into the WASI monorepo by yoshuawuyts · Pull Request #826 · WebAssembly/WASI\">Migrate proposals into the WASI monorepo by yoshuawuyts · Pull Request #826 · WebAssembly/WASI</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">This is the first step in bringing all the proposals into a single repository, AKA creating a WASI monorepo. This was done in a similar way to bytecodealliance/wasmtime#11815 using the git-filter-r...</div></div></div>",
