    {
        "content": "<p>that's marked closed by <a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/commit/2f08b9c03709a0ad6eae0714e3b49e84411b64a9\">https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/commit/2f08b9c03709a0ad6eae0714e3b49e84411b64a9</a> which obviously has nothing to do with blockchain.</p>\n<div class=\"message_embed\"><a class=\"message_embed_image\" href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/commit/2f08b9c03709a0ad6eae0714e3b49e84411b64a9\" style=\"background-image: url(&quot;https://uploads.zulipusercontent.&quot;)\"></a><div class=\"data-container\"><div class=\"message_embed_title\"><a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/commit/2f08b9c03709a0ad6eae0714e3b49e84411b64a9\" title=\"Document fields-get return value when the key is not present · WebAssembly/WASI@2f08b9c\">Document fields-get return value when the key is not present · WebAssembly/WASI@2f08b9c</a></div><div class=\"message_embed_description\">Resolves #56</div></div></div>",
