    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"315881\">Jacob Lifshay</span> <a href=\"#narrow/channel/219900-wasi/topic/PSA.3A.20WASI.20monorepo.20migration.20is.20now.20complete/near/560316730\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>as I mentioned <a href=\"https://github.com/WebAssembly/WASI/pull/826#issuecomment-3577093416\">here</a>, the migration inadvertently closed a bunch of unrelated issues since they happen to share the issue numbers with issues from the original repos that a commit mentioned as closing.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>thanks for catching that; that's really unfortunate - I'll go through them now to try and restore them, starting with the issues you've linked!</p>",
